# KivaLens Companion browser-extension integration (optional).
#
# Set this to the Companion extension's id to turn the integration ON: the companion UI
# appears (Options card + "Detect with Companion" in the lender-ID modal) and KivaLens reads
# your exact Kiva data through it. Leave it UNSET and the extension is not referenced or
# mentioned anywhere on the site.
#
# Find the id at chrome://extensions (unpacked dev build) or use the published Web Store id.
# Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_. Use .env.local (gitignored) for a dev id and
# .env.production for the published id.
#
# VITE_COMPANION_EXT_ID=your_extension_id_here
